    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏交流群：614389592</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你会扮演一位送货员，在城市中遇到各种角色和事件，并做出自己的判断和选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在做出选择之后，你的各项属性会根据你的选择所获得的结果变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/30c3d1e7d38d9621bdcf37f2cca18742.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当属性归零或者过多时，会迎来不好的结局或发生某些特别的事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >属性变化并不是瞬时的，它会随时间缓慢的变化，以让你有应对意外事件的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/0c42295f356a9e6a56601c904a832175.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比如你可以放弃当前事件，把身体交给另外一个人格，她会帮你处理好一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交给另外一个人格之后，当前事件会被中断，一切的属性的变化也会被中止。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/564b7dcf607002537b7515ac718da9f4.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放弃是有代价的，你会因此损失一些属性，但与此同时，你的等级会上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等级会在一些事件中起到至关重要的作用，决定了事件的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/0aafb6fa382bf26f119d1af9656d6016.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到30天时，会发生某个事件，也许你会就此达成某些结局，也许你会因此回到第一天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总之，角色们的命运就掌握在你的选择之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.poster.avif?t=1771997806\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.webm?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252960/extras/318203ce3dcb740eed7a4260ec8bd395.mp4?t=1771997806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏在研发过程中结合了一定的AI技术支持，如您对此有特殊偏好或顾虑，还请酌情选择是否体验。感谢您的理解与支持。</p></li></ul>",
